        <updateDate>2005-09-08T20:21:07Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Amends the Internal Revenue Code to permit taxpayers in chapter 11 bankruptcy proceedings initiated before July 28, 2005, who have asbestos-related liabilities exceeding $250 million, to elect not to reduce their net operating losses by amounts discharged in such proceedings.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
